22 The funds provided by this bond issue, in the amount of $45,000,000, will be used to
33 strengthen and expand infrastructure investments in the State's agricultural, food and forest
44 products economy; to support the State's dairy sector; to protect working farmland; and for
55 farmer disaster relief.
